WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:06.976
(Piano)

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.360
How many times have you changed a decision

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:12.080
to forgive someone

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.376
after being determined not to

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:16.816
with the influence of a tune?

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:20.616
(Piano)

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:23.856
How many situations
have you felt melancholic

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:25.496
and yet good about something?

00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:29.856
(Piano)

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.256
How many times have you felt